abstract.p:
Constructed longwave radiation data using remote sensing observations.  Available are monthly mean and 0.25 degree by 0.25 degree grid data over about 10 years (1990-1999).  Data variables are upward and downward long wave radiation fluxes at sea surface (W/m
2
).  Data sources include: GMS/VISSR,COADS,MCSST,BSRN, and NCEP Reanalysis
